ufu icon-hl-trusted-source-after"><span class=3D"sro">Trusted Source</span>=
</span></a><span></span></hl-trusted-source> suggests they may have health =
benefits. However, they do not provide the protein or other nutrition you n=
eed in the long term.</p></div><div><p>People have also used potatoes as a =
survival food, but eating only potatoes would likely have a negative effect=
